  "literalTranslation": {
    "wordAligned": "and-complete the Hajj -the pilgrimage and-the 'Umrah for-Allah. then-if you were prevented so-what was easy from the sacrificial animal. and do not shave your heads until the sacrificial animal reaches -its place [of slaughter]. then-whoever was among you sick or with him harm from his head so a ransom from fasting or charity or sacrifice. then-if you were secure so whoever benefited with the 'Umrah to the Hajj so what was easy from the sacrificial animal. then-whoever not found so fasting three days in the Hajj and seven if you return. those ten complete. that for-whoever not was his family present -the mosque the sacred. and fear Allah and know that Allah severe [in] punishment."
  },
